Class NetRunner

Namespace
Nebula
Assembly
Nebula.dll

The primary network manager for server and client. NetRunner handles the ENet stream and passing that data to the correct objects. For more information on what kind of data is sent and received on what channels, see NetRunner.ENetChannelId.

[ScriptPath("res://addons/Nebula/Core/NetRunner.cs")]
public class NetRunner : Node, IDisposable

PhysicsTicksPerNetworkTick

This determines how fast the network sends data. When physics runs at 60 ticks per second, then at 2 PhysicsTicksPerNetworkTick, the network runs at 30hz.

public const int PhysicsTicksPerNetworkTick = 2
